title: Defense saves the day in Denver; Broncos beat Vikings 23-20
text:
> Sports Defense saves the day in Denver; Broncos beat Vikings 23-20 Minnesota Vikings quarterback Teddy Bridgewater (5) is sacked by Denver Broncos outside linebacker Von Miller (58) outside linebacker DeMarcus Ware (94) and defensive end Malik Jackson (97) during the first half of an NFL football game Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015, in Denver. (AP Photo/Joe Mahoney)
